Eace KENT, Appellant, v. W. W. HARRISON, U. S. Marshal for the Northern District of Florida, Appellee. No. 7188. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. Jan. 19, 1934. Rehearing Denied Feb. 10, 1934. R. P. Reese, of Pensacola, Fla., for appel-lan£_ George Earl Hoffman, U. S. Atty., of Pensacola, Fla., for appellee.

Before BRYAN, SIBLEY, and WALKER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment is affirmed.
